<p>Our research aims to explain why animals (termites) behave in the way you observed, from all four different approach, <em>mechanism</em>, <em>development</em>, <em>function</em>, and <em>evolutionary history</em>. We put special focus on the last component. Some example projects are below (for a full list of publications, see <a href="../publication">Publication</a>).</p>

<!-- section break -->
